{"tid":951333,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚幣少爺上蘋果LIVE :O","createTime":"2018-12-22T09:04:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T09:12:19.000Z","uid":129225,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"95640cb31c196a5b067ada3a57e6af2ee4e7f18e","tid":951333,"uid":129225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T09:04:28.000Z","msg":"【你問我答9:30pm LIVE】老千定財神？幣少爺踩上《蘋果》接受網民挑機<br />\n<br />\n一場「銀紙雨」，令「幣少爺」黃鉦傑的名字變得街知巷聞。<br />\n<br />\n聲稱靠炒Bitcoin起家，揸跑車、住豪宅，黃鉦傑過去一年在社交網站炫富之餘，亦高調推銷礦機，保守估計已集資逾2000萬元；近期又轉為宣傳自家加密貨幣Filecash Coin，藉派錢、捐錢等「出位」行徑作另類宣傳，成功搶佔各大媒體版面。<br />\n<br />\n有人視他為指路明燈，甘心將畢生積蓄投資高風險加密貨幣，只求早著先機一朝發達；更多人斥責他為騙子，胡亂吹噓利用監管漏洞歛財，坐等有日身敗名裂。<br />\n<br />\n今晚9點半，黃鉦傑將會踩上《蘋果》直播節目《你問我答》，坐在鏡頭面前接受網民質詢。是龍還是蟲，是財神抑或老千，你問，佢答。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181221/large/1545389735_abb1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181221%2Flarge%2F1545389735_abb1.jpg&h=84b03405&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181222/59056530\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181222%2F59056530&d=cm2aClcYNw%2Fqjlfy3CxUbQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=a8ee706a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181222%2F59056530&h=8765e09e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181222/59056530</a>"},{"pid":"ace7798ef71e30d9aa0c6b8be2026c64f3880b3d","tid":951333,"uid":227000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T09:05:30.000Z","msg":"唔回答<br />\n唔知道<br />\n唔回應<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8304888e56e806b3e12c65f240f293415689a861","tid":951333,"uid":42815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T09:06:38.000Z","msg":"老千"}